All were misunderstandings before.

8
00:00:43,840 --> 00:00:45,039
Everyone misunderstood Linglong.

9
00:00:46,000 --> 00:00:47,640
Now the snake demon has been tamed by me.

10
00:00:53,479 --> 00:00:54,119
Mr. Lin.

11
00:00:54,600 --> 00:00:55,439
Miss Linglong.

12
00:00:55,840 --> 00:00:56,359
I

